long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,es,et,fa,fi,f:
🚀 Effortlessly scrape Indeed jobs data!

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Open an Indeed job search result page.
2️⃣ Click open our extension, then click the Export button.
3️⃣ Done! Sit back and just wait a moment, let our extension handle the rest.

🔥 Key Features:
1️⃣ Run in the background without waiting for finish.
2️⃣ Export on multiple job search result pages simultaneous.
3️⃣ Export jobs data for current search result to a csv file, data include: Job Tile, Job Id, Job Url, Company Name, Location, Formatted Range Salary, Min Salary, Max Salary, Salary Type, Job Type, Job Shifts, Job Remote, Job Benefits, Job Schedules, Job Requirements, Apply Count, Company Rating, Company Review Count, Create Time, Publish Time, Description Show HTML, Job Apply Url.

🎯 Targeted Users: numerous parties, including HR managers, recruiters, and business owners  alike.

💡 Benefit from our dedicated support team! We're here to assist you at every step and provide prompt, knowledgeable help.

💪 Take control of your jobs data management and make informed decisions with Indeed Jobs Exporter today!

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Indeed ❗️🔒
long.en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es_419,pt_BR,pt_PT,:
🚀 Effortlessly scrape Indeed jobs data from indeed.com to Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Go to the indeed.com jobs search page.
2️⃣ Perform a search, then click the "Start" button on extension popup.
3️⃣ Choose to download from the data scraping pop-up or the task list on extension.

🌳 What jobs data can I extract using this tool?
jobTitle, jobId, jobUrl, companyName, location, formattedRangeSalary, minSalary, maxSalary, salaryType, jobType, jobShifts, jobRemote, jobBenefits, jobSchedules, createTime, publishTime, applyUrl, applyCount, companyRating, companyReviewCount, jobRequirements and so on.

🎯 Targeted Users: numerous parties, including HR managers, recruiters, and business owners  alike.
